EN: They tried to change their lifestyle to improve their levels of health.

ZH: 我们需要试着适应新的环境。
EN: We need to try to adapt to the new environment.

ZH: 她试着安慰我，告诉我一切都会好起来的。
EN: She tried to comfort me, telling me that everything would be alright.

ZH: 请你试着不要生气，冷静下来再说。
EN: Please try not to get angry, calm down before speaking.

